Don’t miss the launch ( September 21) of @iownow_official a project aimed at creating a more equitable society. Here’s why they’re amazing 👽👉🏽

This creates a more just society at the base level, and as a result solves many of the 
problems we face in urban environments today.

To put the money where our mouth is we give 2/3 of our revenue of each collection drop to local grassroots non-profits to create a positive impact that is direct and truly reaches 
those in need. 

All of our products are economically and ecologically sustainably made in the EU, frommaterials that are recycled and/or recyclable, making our brand fully circular.

To not add anything to the 93 million tons of over-produced clothing that ends on alandfill every year, we strictly offer direct-to-consumer pre-order. This way we makesure to not use a single resource in vein.
